                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "8kkxw",
                      "name": "edH1",
                      "fill": "#1A1A1A",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "2 技术方案",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 24,
                      "fontWeight": "700"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "Cu3jm",
                      "name": "edP1",
                      "fill": "#333333",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "本章详细阐述系统整体技术方案，包括系统架构设计、核心功能模块规划以及关键技术选型依据。方案设计遵循高可用、高性能、可扩展的原则，确保系统能够满足甲方在工业数据采集、智能分析和决策支持方面的核心需求。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "tNhGL",
                      "name": "edH2",
                      "fill": "#1A1A1A",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "2.1 系统架构设计",
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 20,
                      "fontWeight": "600"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "odVJL",
                      "name": "edP2",
                      "fill": "#333333",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "系统采用分层微服务架构，由数据采集层、数据处理层、业务逻辑层和展示层组成。各层之间通过标准化 API 接口进行通信，确保系统的松耦合性和可维护性。数据采集层负责与各类工业设备和传感器的对接，支持 OPC UA、MQTT 等主流工业通信协议。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "Inter",
                      "fontSize": 14,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
